        "title": "Mathjax, pseudocode 사용법",
        "excerpt":"조건  github page, Jekyll theme   사용방법  수식 적용방법은 inline, outline의 경우,  $$[수식]$$  을 이용한다. (psuedocode.js 때문에 그런지 $ 하나로 안됨)   - Fomula Case  \\(\\sum_{i=0}^n i^2 = \\frac{(n^2+n)(2n+1)}{6}\\)   \\[\\begin{align*}   &amp; \\phi(x,y) = \\phi \\left(\\sum_{i=1}^n x_ie_i, \\sum_{j=1}^n y_je_j \\right)   = \\sum_{i=1}^n \\sum_{j=1}^n x_i y_j \\phi(e_i, e_j) = \\\\   &amp; (x_1, \\ldots, x_n) \\left( \\begin{array}{ccc}       \\phi(e_1, e_1) &amp; \\cdots &amp; \\phi(e_1, e_n) \\\\       \\vdots &amp; \\ddots &amp; \\vdots \\\\       \\phi(e_n, e_1) &amp; \\cdots &amp; \\phi(e_n, e_n)     \\end{array} \\right)   \\left( \\begin{array}{c}       y_1 \\\\       \\vdots \\\\       y_n     \\end{array} \\right) \\end{align*}\\]  $$\\sum_{i=0}^n i^2 = \\frac{(n^2+n)(2n+1)}{6}$$  $$ \\begin{align*}   &amp; \\phi(x,y) = \\phi \\left(\\sum_{i=1}^n x_ie_i, \\sum_{j=1}^n y_je_j \\right)   = \\sum_{i=1}^n \\sum_{j=1}^n x_i y_j \\phi(e_i, e_j) = \\\\   &amp; (x_1, \\ldots, x_n) \\left( \\begin{array}{ccc}       \\phi(e_1, e_1) &amp; \\cdots &amp; \\phi(e_1, e_n) \\\\       \\vdots &amp; \\ddots &amp; \\vdots \\\\       \\phi(e_n, e_1) &amp; \\cdots &amp; \\phi(e_n, e_n)     \\end{array} \\right)   \\left( \\begin{array}{c}       y_1 \\\\       \\vdots \\\\       y_n     \\end{array} \\right) \\end{align*} $$   - Algorithm Case        % This quicksort algorithm is extracted from Chapter 7, Introduction to Algorithms (3rd edition)     \\begin{algorithm}     \\caption{Quicksort}     \\begin{algorithmic}     \\PROCEDURE{Quicksort}{$A, p, r$}         \\IF{$p &lt; r$}              \\STATE $q = $ \\CALL{Partition}{$A, p, r$}             \\STATE \\CALL{Quicksort}{$A, p, q - 1$}             \\STATE \\CALL{Quicksort}{$A, q + 1, r$}         \\ENDIF     \\ENDPROCEDURE     \\PROCEDURE{Partition}{$A, p, r$}         \\STATE $x = A[r]$         \\STATE $i = p - 1$         \\FOR{$j = p$ \\TO $r - 1$}             \\IF{$A[j] &lt; x$}                 \\STATE $i = i + 1$                 \\STATE exchange                 $A[i]$ with $A[j]$             \\ENDIF             \\STATE exchange $A[i]$ with $A[r]$         \\ENDFOR     \\ENDPROCEDURE     \\end{algorithmic}     \\end{algorithm}   &lt;pre id=\"quicksort\" style=\"display:hidden;\"&gt;     % This quicksort algorithm is extracted from Chapter 7, Introduction to Algorithms (3rd edition)     \\begin{algorithm}     \\caption{Quicksort}     \\begin{algorithmic}     \\PROCEDURE{Quicksort}{$A, p, r$}         \\IF{$p &lt; r$}              \\STATE $q = $ \\CALL{Partition}{$A, p, r$}             \\STATE \\CALL{Quicksort}{$A, p, q - 1$}             \\STATE \\CALL{Quicksort}{$A, q + 1, r$}         \\ENDIF     \\ENDPROCEDURE     \\PROCEDURE{Partition}{$A, p, r$}         \\STATE $x = A[r]$         \\STATE $i = p - 1$         \\FOR{$j = p$ \\TO $r - 1$}             \\IF{$A[j] &lt; x$}                 \\STATE $i = i + 1$                 \\STATE exchange                 $A[i]$ with $A[j]$             \\ENDIF             \\STATE exchange $A[i]$ with $A[r]$         \\ENDFOR     \\ENDPROCEDURE     \\end{algorithmic}     \\end{algorithm} &lt;/pre&gt;  &lt;!-- 알고리즘 렌더링--&gt; &lt;script&gt;     pseudocode.renderElement(document.getElementById(\"quicksort\")); &lt;/script&gt;      문법의 내용은 다음의 사이트들을 참고한다.      LaTex docs   간단한 사용 예시   모르는 기호를 LaTex 문법으로 맞춰 제안   온라인 LaTeX 수식 확인 가능 사이트 -상당히 유용!  ","categories": ["etc","Others"],
